| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1471 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: f4ebbcca-e2c8-5595-912d-0ae9c4fe28bb"
